sequenceDiagram
    participant Application
    participant OpenTelemetry
    participant Serilog
    participant Dashboard as Aspire Dashboard

    Application->>OpenTelemetry: Generate Traces and Metrics
    Application->>Serilog: Capture Structured Logs
    Serilog-->>OpenTelemetry: Bridge via writeToProviders
    OpenTelemetry->>Dashboard: Export via OTLP (gRPC)

    Note right of OpenTelemetry: OTLP Exporter
    Note right of Serilog: Console Sink + OTel Bridge
    Note right of Dashboard: Logs, Traces, Metrics in one UI
